Name: Date Write
About the game: Date Write, Mehmetcik is a game of different missions and story-oriented FPS in order to clear the terrorist formations in the neighboring country. About Our Hero: Mehmetcik, the name given to the Turkish soldier with a sense of love. Every soldier is actually a Mehmetcik. Therefore, it symbolizes the whole Republic of Turkey. Story: Civil war continues in Syria. Terrorist groups of different names have taken over the area. The city of Afrin, too. The Republic of Turkey has launched a cross-border operation to ensure the security of the region. Our hero, Mehmetcik, takes a special active role. With our Unmanned Aerial Vehicles and land operations, the region is cleared of terrorists, and the city begins to fight fearlessly for security. Gameplay: The rule of the game is left to the player. The player determines the fate of the game with his own strategies.
